# ğŸš€ QuickGPT

QuickGPT is an AI-powered web platform that helps creators, developers, and marketers generate **content, code, and visuals** from a single dashboard.  
It also includes a **personalized AI assistant** that understands user intent and provides context-aware insights from user-generated content.

