### ğŸ§  AI Assistant (Personalized)
- Intent-aware responses (greetings, help, summaries, insights)
- Context-driven answers using user-generated content
- Embeddings-based semantic understanding
- Fast responses for common queries
- Learns from past creations and interactions

### ğŸ¨ AI Image Tools
- Text-to-image generation  
- Background removal & replacement  
- Object removal  

### ğŸ” Authentication & Billing
- Secure authentication with **Clerk**
- Subscription & credit-based usage system

